keyword:
	keyword: Terraform
	match: terraform
	reminder:
		{
		 handle_action_rt(to:"terraform", "Draw")
		} a card. You may put it onto the battlefield tapped if it’s a land.
	rules:
		nb. still drawn.
		nb. put from hand.
	mode: custom
keyword:
	keyword: Accelerate
	match: Accelerate <atom-param>cost</atom-param>
	reminder:
		You may cast this spell for its accelerate cost any time you could cast an instant. If you do, {
		 if has_pt()
		 then "it can’t block this turn and is"
		 else "it’s"
		} sacrificed at the beginning of your next upkeep.
	rules: nb. an alt-cost.
	mode: 
keyword:
	keyword: Accelerate
	match: Resuscitate <atom-param>cost</atom-param>
	reminder: You may cast this permanent from your graveyard for its resuscitate cost. It enters with a finality counter.
	rules:
		nb. an alt-cost.
		
		If a permanent with a finality counter would die, exile it instead.
	mode: 
keyword:
	keyword: Finance-a-Spell
	match: finance
	reminder: Spells cast by spending at least four mana or with mana value 4+ are financed.
	rules:
		eg. Whenever you finance a spell, …
		eg. At the beginning of each end step, if you financed a spell this turn, …
	mode: custom
keyword:
	keyword: Perform-a-Deed
	match: a deed
	reminder: Targeting yourself, a teammate, anything you/they control, and cards in your graveyards or exile zones is a deed.
	rules:
		eg. Whenever you perform a deed, … This ability triggers only once each turn.
		eg. At the beginning of each end step, if you performed a deed this turn, …
